snippet.title: Meghan Markle Parody- ENGAGEMENT Interview. CLUELESS or CALCULATED?
snippet.description:
Hi! my name is Carla Yang, Welcome to my channel!

Today's video is a Meghan Markle parody, based on her engagement interview with her now husband, Prince Harry. I hope you have fun watching this video, and if so, consider liking and subscribing!

Disclaimer: this video was created for entertainment purposes only. 

Feel free to check these links out!
Engagement interview:

www.youtube.com/watch?v=LQicq60aJaw&list=PL3b067p5TTpPahXU_PnUGIJxJDzVjCVAn&index=8

Ring change:

www.dailymail.co.uk/femail/article-7178695/Royal-expert-slams-Meghan-Markle-updating-engagement-ring-band-piece-history.html

#meghanmarkle #princeharry
Thank you for watching and feel free to share what your thoughts are on this video! All feedback appreciated! 

Stay tuned, and stay safe!
